{"type":"message","id":"c8296f36","parentId":"e14471f7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:23:21.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see there are active sessions. The user (Khuowgn) is asking \"báo cáo đâu\" (where's the report). Looking at the sessions, there's an active subagent in the direct session labeled \"DTLX BE Fix & Test\" that's currently cloning a repo with a GitLab token. Let me check what that subagent is doing.\n\nAlso, looking at the queued messages, these are system exec completion notifications from DTLX backend operations - MongoDB indexes, role seeding, API tests, etc. These are just automated cron/system tasks completing.\n\nThe user seems to be asking where their report is. Let me check the direct session to see what's happening with the \"DTLX BE Fix & Test\" subagent that's currently running.","thinkingSignature":"d5c2d86107ec37ae16db93017e092fa71a730bb462945978a46f7140be256aa9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9kbdnsq86zes_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","limit":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":4897,"output":208,"cacheRead":19375,"cacheWrite":1995,"totalTokens":26475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776140593874,"responseId":"062cf4332088e818f18905facb3c7d5f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"563fccb2","parentId":"c8296f36","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:23:26.754Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9kbdnsq86zes_1","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Now I need to also fix the sessions.json for senior-backend - the existing sessions have the old model cached. When new sessions spawn, they'll pick up the new default from models.json. But existing sessions will still have the old model. That's fine - new subagents will use DEV.\\n\\nLet me now restart the DTLX group with the fixed model config.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"✅ Đã fix model config. Bây giờ restart DTLX group:\\n\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_wp5vmufqe117_1\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_spawn\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"task\": \"You are the DTLX ecosystem orchestrator (group -5168104492). Your job: test API module auth on ahv-dtlx-backend.\\n\\n## Project\\n- **GitLab:** ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend (77055841), ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend (77055851)\\n- **Bot:** @thuowgn_bot in group -5168104492\\n\\n## Current state\\n- DTLX FE: port 3000 running\\n- DTLX BE: Build failed — TypeScript errors on feature/clean-architecture-migration branch\\n  - Error: interface mismatch (data vs docs, limit vs itemsPerPage)\\n- deploy-be subagent: timed out (SIGKILL)\\n\\n## Your tasks\\n1. Clone/check ahv-dtlx-backend \\n2. Run `yarn build` to see ALL TypeScript errors\\n3. Fix them systematically\\n4. Build successfully\\n5. Start BE server  \\n6. Test API auth endpoints:\\n   - POST /api/v1/auth/register\\n   - POST /api/v1/auth/login\\n   - GET /api/v1/auth/profile\\n\\n## IMPORTANT: Use AHV-Holding-DEV model (NOT TroLy)\\nThe TroLy model is broken (500 providerSpecificData errors). Use DEV.\\n\\n## Rules\\n- Follow Git Workflow: branch-per-task + MR for Lead review  \\n- Commit with [Khuowgn]-senior-backend identity\\n- Log progress to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\\n- Respond to @thuowgn_bot mentions in the group\\n\\nStart immediately — clone the repo, build, fix TS errors.\",\n            \"label\": \"DTLX BE Fix & Test\",\n            \"runtime\": \"subagent\",\n            \"agentId\": \"master-orchestrator\",\n            \"model\": \"ahvholding/AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n            \"mode\": \"run\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1776140485038,\n      \"responseId\": \"062cf3c6a4797996964de75f7f1dc9ae\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"b77492c3\",\n        \"seq\": 547\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The subagent has been spawned with AHV-Holding-DEV model. Let me update Lead on what happened.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"✅ **Đã fix root cause + restart task:**\\n\\n**Nguyên nhân gốc:** Model `AHV-Holding-TroLy` bị lỗi 500 trên mọi request — tất cả backend subagents spawn đều dùng TroLy → fail hết.\\n\\n**Đã fix:**\\n- ✅ senior-backend: DEV first\\n- ✅ senior-frontend: DEV first\\n- ✅ ui-ux-pro-max: DEV first\\n- ✅ senior-devops: DEV first\\n- ✅ senior-qa: DEV first\\n- ✅ planner: DEV first\\n\\n**DTLX task đã restart** với model `AHV-Holding-DEV`. Orbis đợi kết quả.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1776140508858,\n      \"responseId